 (aa) a person described in the application for the licence as participating in the management or control of a warehouse covered by the licence ceases to do so; or

 (b) in the case of a licence held by a partnership—there is a change in the membership of the partnership; or

 (ba) in the case of a licence held by a company—any of the following events occurs:

